OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774624292
OL,3,CMan convicted of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cex in 'frenzied' knife attack at
OL,5,Cworkplace
OL,7,FA 38-year-old man who stabbed his ex-
OL,8,Fpartner 17 times in a "frenzied" knife
OL,9,Fattack at the office building where
OL,10,Fshe worked has been found guilty of
OL,11,Fher attempted murder.
OL,13,FAnwar Ashraf was convicted following a
OL,14,Ftrial at Winchester Crown Court
OL,15,Ffollowing the attack on Carla Skeites
OL,16,Fon the premises at 3600 Parkway in
OL,17,FWhiteley, Hampshire, at about 9am on
OL,18,FApril 30 2025.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
