FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774624292
OL,3,CMan convicted of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cex in 'frenzied' knife attack at
OL,5,Cworkplace
OL,7,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fwounding with intent to cause grievous
OL,9,Fbodily harm and possession of a knife,
OL,10,Fbut he had denied that he wanted to
OL,11,Fkill her.
OL,13,FGiles Bedloe, prosecuting, told the
OL,14,Ftrial that Ashraf had become
OL,15,F"obsessed" with Ms Skeites and accused
OL,16,Fher of "cheating" on him, despite the
OL,17,Frelationship having ended.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@JO]xD@HOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
