OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774624292
OL,3,CMan convicted of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cex in 'frenzied' knife attack at
OL,5,Cworkplace
OL,7,FMr Bedloe said that on the morning of
OL,8,Fthe attack, Ms Skeites was preparing
OL,9,Ffor a training presentation at the
OL,10,Ftravel agency where she worked when
OL,11,Fshe received a message that Ashraf was
OL,12,Foutside the building and had asked to
OL,13,Fsee her.
OL,15,FHe said that Ms Skeites went to see
OL,16,Fhim and after a "brief conversation,
OL,17,Fshe told him to leave her alone and go
OL,18,Faway" before "randomly he hugged her"
OL,19,Fand he followed her back into the
OL,20,Flobby as she tried to move away from
OL,21,Fhim.
OL,26,@xD@QOUzD@EO]zD@NOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774624292
OL,3,CMan convicted of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cex in 'frenzied' knife attack at
OL,5,Cworkplace
OL,7,FThe prosecutor added: "She was telling
OL,8,Fhim he needed to leave. Suddenly he
OL,9,Fsaid: 'I have a knife' and showed her
OL,10,Fa black-handled kitchen knife."
OL,12,FMr Bedloe said that the victim later
OL,13,Fdescribed the attack, saying: "Before
OL,14,FI knew it, he was stabbing me."
OL,16,FHe continued: "She asked him to stop
OL,17,Fbut he didn't, then this frenzied
OL,18,Fattack stopped as soon as it started
OL,19,Fas other people came to help."
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@_O]uD@_OUvD@_O]xD@OOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774624292
OL,3,CMan convicted of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cex in 'frenzied' knife attack at
OL,5,Cworkplace
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said that the defendant
OL,8,Fwas restrained by members of the
OL,9,Fpublic, with one man kicking his legs
OL,10,Fto knock him over before blocking his
OL,11,Fexit.
OL,13,FAnother worker attempted to administer
OL,14,Ffirst aid and described the "terrified
OL,15,Flook" on Ms Skeites' face.
OL,17,FMr Bedloe added: "Carla Skeites was
OL,18,Frushed to hospital as she sustained
OL,19,Fmultiple injuries as a result of this
OL,20,Ffrenzied attack, including 17
OL,21,Findividual stab wounds."
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@EO]yD@ROU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774624292
OL,3,CMan convicted of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cex in 'frenzied' knife attack at
OL,5,Cworkplace
OL,7,FThe court was told that as Ashraf was
OL,8,Fdetained by police, he said: "What
OL,9,Fwould you do if your partner cheated
OL,10,Fon you, how would you react?"
OL,12,FMr Bedloe added: "He admitted what he
OL,13,Fhad done, he said he only wanted to
OL,14,Fscare her, he didn't want to kill her."
OL,16,FAshraf, previously of Southsea, will
OL,17,Fbe sentenced on June 5.
OL,26,@pD@^OUrD@]O]tD@ROUvD@gO]
